OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1773951077
OL,3,CFirst-time buyer 'forced to abandon
OL,4,Cdream home' after law firm collapse
OL,6,FA Butterworths Solicitors client says
OL,7,Fshe felt like she had no other option
OL,8,Fbut to abandon the purchase of her
OL,9,F'dream home' after the collapse of the
OL,10,Flaw firm earlier this year.
OL,12,FMarie Latimer is one of hundreds of
OL,13,Fclients who was left in limbo after
OL,14,Fthe solicitors, owned by PM Law Group,
OL,15,Fclosed suddenly on 2 February.
OL,17,FThe Solicitors Regulation Authority
OL,18,F(SRA) says it is is investigating
OL,19,Fpotential fraud, including the
OL,20,Fmisappropriation of customers' money.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1773951077
OL,3,CFirst-time buyer 'forced to abandon
OL,4,Cdream home' after law firm collapse
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Border about her
OL,7,Fexperience, Ms Latimer said: "You just
OL,8,Fdidn't know what was coming next, what
OL,9,Fto do or where to turn.
OL,11,F"It wasn't fair on the sellers to keep
OL,12,Fthem waiting and waiting for the
OL,13,Funknown from what was going on."
OL,15,FShe currently has no fixed address and
OL,16,Fis living with her brother, a
OL,17,Ffrustration for her.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1773951077
OL,3,CFirst-time buyer 'forced to abandon
OL,4,Cdream home' after law firm collapse
OL,6,FShe said: "Everything's been packed
OL,7,Faway since November and I just want to
OL,8,Funpack and get my own place and get
OL,9,Fsettled."
OL,11,FShe's not alone, as the SRA says the
OL,12,FPM Law Group was made up of 11
OL,13,Fcompanies and more than 30 trading
OL,14,Fnames.
OL,16,FIn Cumbria, Butterworths Solicitors
OL,17,Fhad four branches in Carlisle,
OL,18,FPenrith, Kendal and Hensingham.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1773951077
OL,3,CFirst-time buyer 'forced to abandon
OL,4,Cdream home' after law firm collapse
OL,6,FThe SRA says that 17,000 clients
OL,7,Facross the PM Law Group have been
OL,8,Femailed with next steps and they've
OL,9,Fstated that they've returned #9
OL,10,Fmillion of money held by the firm so
OL,11,Ffar.
OL,13,FThe regulator has also said: "When we
OL,14,Fintervene into a firm, we use another
OL,15,Ffirm as our agents to carry out work
OL,16,Ffor us.
OL,18,F"In this intervention, that firm is
OL,19,FGordons LLP."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1773951077
OL,3,CFirst-time buyer 'forced to abandon
OL,4,Cdream home' after law firm collapse
OL,6,FThe SRA believes most customers have
OL,7,Fbeen contacted and if they haven't
OL,8,Fthey're asking clients to get in touch.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, South Yorkshire Police
OL,11,Fsaid: "We can confirm we have received
OL,12,Fa referral from Report Fraud regarding
OL,13,Freports received in relation to
OL,14,FSheffield based law firm PM Law.
OL,16,F"This is currently under review by our
OL,17,FEconomic Crime unit to determine next
OL,18,Fsteps and the most appropriate agency
OL,19,Fto take this forward."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
